### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### API de Biblioteca - Tests con REST Client (VS Code)
### Instala la extensión "REST Client" para ejecutarlos
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@base = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = PEGA_TU_TOKEN_AQUI

# ─── AUTH ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Registrar usuario
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@correo.es",
  "name": "Usuario Test",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 2. Login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@biblioteca.es",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. Obtener perfil propio
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── BOOKS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4. Listar libros
GET {{base}}/books

###

### 5. Listar con filtros
GET {{base}}/books?genre=Fantasía&available=true&page=1&limit=5

###

### 6. Detalle de un libro
GET {{base}}/books/1

###

### 7. Crear libro (requiere rol LIBRARIAN o ADMIN)
POST {{base}}/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "978-84-999-0001-1",
  "title": "Cien años de soledad",
  "author": "Gabriel García Márquez",
  "genre": "Realismo mágico",
  "publishedYear": 1967,
  "copies": 3
}

###

### 8. Actualizar libro
PUT {{base}}/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "available": 2
}

###

### 9. Eliminar libro (solo ADMIN)
DELETE {{base}}/books/99
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── LOANS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 10. Mis préstamos
GET {{base}}/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. Todos los préstamos (LIBRARIAN/ADMIN)
GET {{base}}/loans/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 12. Solicitar préstamo
POST {{base}}/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 2
}

###

### 13. Devolver libro
PUT {{base}}/loans/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── REVIEWS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 14. Ver reseñas de un libro
GET {{base}}/books/2/reviews

###

### 15. Crear reseña (solo si has devuelto el libro)
POST {{base}}/books/1/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Una obra maestra de la literatura universal"
}

###

### 16. Eliminar mi reseña
DELETE {{base}}/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
